roversial-ugandan-crude-oil-pipeline?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>产能过剩担忧预示着一个时代的结束，中国钢铁行业面临“悬崖”风险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3261344/chinas-steel-industry-risks-falling-cliff-overcapacity-concerns-point-end-era?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的钢铁产量有所增加，但房地产市场低迷和基础设施支出放缓导致价格大幅下跌，导致产能过剩和贸易紧张。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 04:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3261344/chinas-steel-industry-risks-falling-cliff-overcapacity-concerns-point-end-era?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国大型科技公司：为何许多过度劳累的员工在互联网放缓的情况下辞职创业</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3261117/china-big-tech-why-many-overworked-employees-are-quitting-become-entrepreneurs-amid-internet?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>近年来，中国互联网巨头纷纷裁员，影响了数万人，其中许多人决定自己创业，但结果好坏参半。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 02:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3261117/china-big-tech-why-many-overworked-employees-are-quitting-become-entrepreneurs-amid-internet?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>要恢复金融活力，香港必须真正拥抱多元化</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/hong-kong-opinion/article/3261278/restore-its-financial-dynamism-hong-kong-must-truly-embrace-diversity?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在一系列挫折中，香港在培养新兴市场的外国人才和资本方面仍然停留在过去的状态。通过将自己打造成庆祝创新和多元文化的中心，这座城市可以吸引来自世界各地的顶级专业人士。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 01:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/hong-kong-opinion/article/3261278/restore-its-financial-dynamism-hong-kong-must-truly-embrace-diversity?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>解放军坚持大棒，交换胡萝卜：赖清德就职典礼临近，北京加大对台湾施压</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3261385/beijing-ramps-pressure-taiwan-warplanes-trade-and-travel-policies-william-lais-inauguration-nears?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着台湾当选总统赖清德准备上任，中国大陆发出了复杂的信息，