conomy/economic-indicators/article/3261367/china-wants-sci-fi-industry-led-megahit-3-body-problem-help-tech-make-jump-lightspeed?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>因 Netflix 热播的《三体》而成为人们关注的焦点，中国科幻产业 2023 年收入同比增长 29%，达到 132.9 亿元人民币（156 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 11:30:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3261367/china-wants-sci-fi-industry-led-megahit-3-body-problem-help-tech-make-jump-lightspeed?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>